#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:1
msgid "One-Click Bootstrap"
msgstr "Arranque con un solo clic"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:3
msgid ""
"This page defines the fastest supported path to install and initialize "
"ZeroClaw."
msgstr "Esta página define la ruta más rápida para instalar e inicializar ZeroClaw."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:5
msgid "Last verified: **April 12, 2026**."
msgstr "Última verificación: **12 de abril de 2026**."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:7
msgid "Option 0: Homebrew (macOS/Linuxbrew)"
msgstr "Opción 0: Homebrew (macOS/Linuxbrew)"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:13
msgid "Option A (Recommended): Clone + local script"
msgstr "Opción A (Recomendada): Clonar + script local"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:21
msgid "What it does:"
msgstr "Qué hace:"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:23
msgid "Installs Rust via rustup if missing"
msgstr "Instala Rust a través de rustup si no está presente."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:24
msgid "Validates Rust version against project MSRV"
msgstr "Valida la versión de Rust frente al MSRV del proyecto"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:25
msgid "`cargo install --path . --locked --force`"
msgstr "`cargo install --path . --locked --force`"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:26
msgid "Runs `zeroclaw onboard` (interactive setup wizard)"
msgstr "Ejecuta `zeroclaw onboard` (asistente de configuración interactiva)"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:28
msgid "Option B: Remote one-liner"
msgstr "Opción B: Comando remoto de una sola línea"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:34
msgid ""
"For high-security environments, prefer Option A so you can review the script "
"before execution."
msgstr "Para entornos de alta seguridad, se prefiere la Opción A para que puedas revisar el script antes de su ejecución."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:36
msgid "Build profiles"
msgstr "Perfiles de compilación"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:39
msgid "# full (default features)\n"
msgstr "# completo (características predeterminadas)\n"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:40
msgid "# kernel only (~6.6MB)\n"
msgstr "# solo kernel (~6.6MB)\n"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:41
msgid "# custom\n"
msgstr "# personalizado\n"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:44
msgid ""
"`--minimal` builds the kernel: config, providers, memory, CLI chat. No agent "
"runtime, no channels, no gateway. Ideal for SBCs and containers."
msgstr "`--minimal` compila el kernel: configuración, proveedores, memoria, CLI chat. Sin ejecución de agente, sin canales, sin puerta de enlace. Ideal para SBCs y contenedores."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:46
msgid ""
"`--features` selects specific features. Works alone (adds to defaults) or "
"with `--minimal` (builds from scratch)."
msgstr "`--features` selecciona características específicas. Funciona de forma independiente (agrega a las predeterminadas) o junto con `--minimal` (compila desde cero)."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:48
msgid "To see all available features:"
msgstr "Para ver todas las características disponibles:"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:54
msgid "Testing in isolation"
msgstr "Pruebas en aislamiento"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:56
msgid ""
"Use `--prefix` to install everything into a scratch directory without "
"touching your home:"
msgstr "Utiliza `--prefix` para instalar todo en un directorio temporal sin tocar tu carpeta personal:"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:61
msgid "# Clean up\n"
msgstr "# Limpiar\n"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:66
msgid "Use `--dry-run` to preview what would happen without building:"
msgstr "Usa `--dry-run` para previsualizar lo que sucedería sin construir:"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:72
msgid "Skip onboarding"
msgstr "Omitir la configuración inicial"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:78
msgid "Configure later with `zeroclaw onboard`."
msgstr "Configurar más tarde con `zeroclaw onboard`."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:80
msgid "Uninstall"
msgstr "Desinstalar"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:86
msgid ""
"Removes the binary and optionally the config/data directory (`~/.zeroclaw/`)."
msgstr "Elimina el binario y opcionalmente el directorio de configuración/datos (`~/.zeroclaw/`)."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:88
msgid "Pre-built binaries"
msgstr "Binarios precompilados"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:90
msgid "For pre-built release binaries (no compilation required):"
msgstr "Para binarios de lanzamiento precompilados (sin necesidad de compilación):"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:93
msgid "\"zeroclaw-$(uname -m)*\""
msgstr "`zeroclaw-$(uname -m)*`"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:96
msgid ""
"Or download from [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw/"
"releases/latest)."
msgstr "O descarga desde [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw/releases/latest)."

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:98
msgid "Docker"
msgstr "Docker"

#: src/setup/one-click-bootstrap.md:100
msgid ""
"See the `docker-compose.yml` at the repository root for containerized "
"deployment."
msgstr "Consulta el archivo `docker-compose.yml` en la raíz del repositorio para el despliegue en contenedores."

